Sample letters

Below are a few sample letters from EE, to give you a feel for what is inside. Note that this represents only a tiny selection of the content and the supporting material inside EE, where each letter comes with links to biographies, manuscript and early edition information, annotations of all kinds . . .

Sample lives

Below are a few sample biographical notes from EE. This represents only a tiny selection of the biographical material inside EE, where each biography comes with links to the person's correspondents and their letters, and many have further birth and death details, cross-links to other figures in EE, and links to biographies in other scholarly resources . . .
